Description
-----------
adplay is AdPlug's UNIX console-based frontend.

Prerequisites
-------------
The following libraries are needed in order to compile this program:

Library		Version
-------		-------
adplug		>= 1.1

Installation
------------
See file INSTALL for instructions.

CVS
---
If you checked out from CVS, first run:

./autogen.sh

to generate the build cruft and get the configure script.

Usage
-----
Start adplay with at least one file to be played as parameter. Additional
commandline parameters are explained by typing:

adplay --help

That's all for now. A more detailed doc will follow when i get the time to
write one. Any help is greatly appreciated!

	- Simon Peter <dn.tlp@gmx.net>
